 the terms of debate over the next round of Supreme Court appointments?The contributors-Bruce Ackerman, Jack Balkin, Guido Calabresi, Steven Calabresi, Owen Fiss, Charles Fried, Robert Post, Margaret Jane Radin, Jeffrey Rosen, Jed Rubenfeld, Cass Sunstein, Laurence Tribe, and Mark Tushnet-represent a broad political spectrum. Their reactions to the case are varied and surprising, filled with sparkling argument and spirited debate. This is a must-read book for thoughtful Americans everywhere.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aContested electionszFlorida. 0aPresidentszUnited StatesxElectiony2000. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aAckerman, Bruce, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAckerman, Bruce, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBalkin, Jack M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCalabresi, Guido, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCalabresi, Steven G., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFiss, Owen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFried, Charles, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPost, Robert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRadin, Margaret Jane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRosen, Jeffrey, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRubenfeld, Jed, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSunstein, Cass R., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTribe, Laurence H., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTushnet, Mark, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is par